Package: destim
Type: Package
Title: R package for mobile devices position estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Salgado <david.salgado.fernandez@ine.es>, Luis Sanguiao Sande <luis.sanguiao.sande@ine.es>, Bogdan Oancea <bogdan.oancea@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Bogdan Oancea <bogdan.oancea@gmail.com>
Description: R package for mobile devices position estimation. This package provides functions to estimate the location probability of mobile devices starting from netwrok events using a Hidden Markov model approach.
